xprmtl-03_hide-first-recording-level-v3.patch
    Lars Hanisch <dvb@flensrocker.de>

    Hide the first level of directories in the recordings menu, all recordings
    are stored at the "local" directory

vdr-2.1.6-conf.d-v6.diff
    Lars Hanisch <dvb@flensrocker.de>

    Patch for VDR to support reading its arguments from files.

